{"tid":513637,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"理解係一回事，但感受都係一回事","createTime":"2017-12-29T17:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T06:58:59.000Z","uid":151781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6aa5e26e951ca0e73af07710b6aa24f4cc5e4d","tid":513637,"uid":151781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"自從畢左業後都好耐無見過班中同<br />\n好不容易約到<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當年最friend果堆+老師</span>出嚟食飯<br />\n點知臨出嚟老師先話病，問完一輪大部分人都話照去<br />\n<br />\n過多陣就陸續收到幾個私chat話唔舒服、主角（老師）唔嚟所以唔去等等等等放我飛機<br />\n去到本來訂左位既餐廳又收到幾個話以為老師病左就cancel 所以無出到既message<br />\n最後本來20人變左8個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔好意思同餐廳講我又比多幾個人放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明白因爲主角有事嚟唔到所以大家都唔係好想出嚟，但我真係由幾個星期前開始期待依個gathering <br />\n我都理解部分人係真心因為財政困難等等因素所以決定唔嚟<br />\n但知道咁多位唔會出現果陣真係頹撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位請原諒我收到你地唔去果啲messages 果陣失落得濟無覆到「唔緊要」啦對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依加諗返起我都唔知當初我咁期待做乜勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f4ed6c20a83638953a516ea66c802166d603187c","tid":513637,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"財政困難，食餐飯咋喎"},{"pid":"54f3326e7086fe3484ca68d1bf33658bf326a094","tid":513637,"uid":151781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ed6c20a83638953a516ea66c802166d603187c","tid":513637,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T17:42:09.000Z","ms